In the footage, the 23-year-old Frenchman is seen posing for pictures and giving an interview in which he says: ‘I am here to help the team to win titles – the league, the cup and the Champions League.’

City were waiting to post it on their website once the transfer is completed.

Although negotiations are said to be progressing well on what sources have described as a ‘complicated’ deal, it has not been finalised yet.

